NK010(tha)007:0: phur pa rgyud lugs las mngon rtogs bsdus pa rdo rje bkod pa'i rgyan zhes bya ba bzhugs /
NK010(tha)007:1: de bzhin gshegs pa khrag 'thung gi rgyal po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK010(tha)007:2: bskyed rim gyi gnad dang lha'i mngon rtogs la cung
NK010(tha)007:3: zad nges pa brtan pa'i don du phrin las kyi
NK010(tha)007:4: byang bu shin tu bsdus pa la sbyor dngos rjes
NK010(tha)007:5: gsum gyi / sbyor ba la'ang bdun las /
NK010(tha)007:6: dang po bdun rnam dag ni /
NK010(tha)007:7: rdo rje slob dpon sangs rgyas dpal //
NK010(tha)007:8: dus gsum bzhugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK010(tha)007:9: mchog gsum bsten pa'i zhing gyur la //
NK010(tha)007:10: gnyis med yid kyis skyabs su mchi //
NK010(tha)007:11: dngos 'byor yid kyis rnam sprul pa'i //
NK010(tha)007:12: dag pa'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK010(tha)007:13: dngos grub cho bo gcod pa'i gegs //
NK010(tha)007:14: nyes byas ma lus bshags par bgyi //
NK010(tha)007:15: phyogs bcu 'khor gsum dag pa'i chos //
NK010(tha)007:16: ma chags spyod la rjes yi rang //
NK010(tha)007:17: dag pa'i mtha' bzhi dri ma med //
NK010(tha)007:18: rdzogs pa'i byang chub sems bskyed do //
NK010(tha)007:19: bde gshegs dbang phyug sems can la //
NK010(tha)007:20: dgos pa gsum phyir lus dbul lo //
NK010(tha)007:21: tshe rabs bgrangs pa'i las rnams kun //
NK010(tha)007:22: bsdus te byang chub chen por bsngo //
NK010(tha)007:23: gnyis pa phyi rol pa bskrad pa ni /
NK010(tha)007:24: gtor ma +aa k+aa ros brlabs la /
NK010(tha)007:26: nyon cig bgegs dang logs 'dren tshogs //
NK010(tha)007:27: nga yi bka' las 'da' ma byed //
NK010(tha)007:28: rdo rje gsang ba'i bka' las ni //
NK010(tha)007:29: sdig can gang zhig 'da' byed pa //
NK010(tha)007:30: stobs chen khro bo chen po yis //
NK010(tha)007:31: klad pa tshal ba brgya ru khos //
NK010(tha)007:32: lus kyang dum bu stong du gtub //
NK010(tha)007:33: snying yang tshal pa bdun du gtub //
NK010(tha)007:35: gsum pa mtshams gcad pa ni /
NK010(tha)007:38: khams gsum de bzhin rol pa'i sku //
NK010(tha)007:39: ma lus phur pas thebs zhes bya //
NK010(tha)007:40: gang zhig gnod pa'i tshogs rnams la //
NK010(tha)007:41: rnam par shes pa'i tshogs brgyad nang //
NK010(tha)007:42: rdo rje phur pa mang shar zhing //
NK010(tha)007:43: de yis tshogs brgyad dag par bya //
NK010(tha)007:44: badz+ra k+ai la ya h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)007:46: ye shes lnga ldan bla ma rdo rje 'dzin //
NK010(tha)007:47: rdo rje rigs kyi lha tshogs dgongs su gsol //
NK010(tha)007:48: khrag 'thung khro bo khro mos byin gyis rlobs //
NK010(tha)007:49: bdag gi lus kyis srog gcod ma byin blangs //
NK010(tha)007:50: mi tshangs spyad cing ting 'dzin sku ma gsal //
NK010(tha)007:51: sku yi dam tshig nyams pa mthol lo bshags //
NK010(tha)007:52: +aah bdag gi ngag gis rdzun dang phra ma dang //
NK010(tha)007:53: ngag 'khyal tshig rtsub bzlas brjod grangs ma skyol //
NK010(tha)007:54: rdo rje bzlas pa'i don ni ma rtogs te //
NK010(tha)007:55: gsung gi dam tshig nyams pa mthol lo bshags //
NK010(tha)007:57: bdag gis snod ldan sems can thams cad la //
NK010(tha)007:58: brnab sems gnod sems log lta skyes pa dang //
NK010(tha)007:59: chos nyid zab mo'i don ni ma rtogs te //
NK010(tha)007:60: lta ba thugs kyi dam tshig nyams pa bshags //
NK010(tha)007:62: sems can thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas rgyur //
NK010(tha)007:63: ma rtogs bdag gis barngana dang skyon du bgrangs //
NK010(tha)007:64: sangs rgyas yon tan mtha' yas ma brjod cing //
NK010(tha)007:65: yon tan dam tshig nyams pa mthol lo gshags //
NK010(tha)007:67: sangs rgyas phrin las sna tshogs dpag med kyi //
NK010(tha)007:68: snying rje chen pos sems can don ma byas //
NK010(tha)007:69: bdud rtsi lnga la longs spyod ma nus shing //
NK010(tha)007:70: phrin las dam tshig nyams pa mthol lo bshags //
NK010(tha)007:72: skye ba rnam bzhis bsdus pa'i sems can rnams //
NK010(tha)007:73: chos sku rnam dag dbyings las gzugs skur snang //
NK010(tha)007:74: bde ba chen pos kun las khyab dmigs te //
NK010(tha)007:75: yang dag don ma rtogs pa mthol lo bshags //
NK010(tha)007:76: zhes pas rgyud dag par bya'o //
NK010(tha)007:79: 'phags mchog thugs rjee'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)007:80: khyad par bstan pa'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)007:81: mthu rtsal dbyung ba'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)007:82: byin gyis rlob pa'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)007:83: dbang mchog bskur ba'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)007:84: dngos grub stsol ba'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)007:86: byin chen byin phob bcom ldan 'das //
NK010(tha)007:87: dbang chen dbang bskur bcom ldan 'das //
NK010(tha)007:88: dngos grub mchog stsol bcom ldan 'das //
NK010(tha)007:89: bdag cag las 'bras mchis par mdzod //
NK010(tha)007:90: h+aum h+aum h+aum h+aum gis byin bsdu /
NK010(tha)007:91: bdun pa mchod pa byin brlab ni /
NK010(tha)007:93: snang srid thams cad mchod pa'i sprin //
NK010(tha)007:94: ye shes bdud rtsir byin brlabs pas //
NK010(tha)007:95: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod rdzas kun //
NK010(tha)007:96: kun bzang rnam 'phrul chen por gyur //
NK010(tha)007:105: sman gtor rak+ta'i sngags lan gsum re brjod /
NK010(tha)007:106: gnyis pa dngos gzhi la bcu gcig las /
NK010(tha)007:109: rdo rje khros pas zhe sdang gcod //
NK010(tha)007:110: mtshon chen sngon po 'bar ba yis //
NK010(tha)007:111: nam mkha'i dkyil nas thigs pa shar //
NK010(tha)007:112: snying gi go ru bsgom par bya //
NK010(tha)007:114: snying rjes bsgral ba'i dam tshig ni //
NK010(tha)007:115: bsad cing mnan pa ma yin te //
NK010(tha)007:116: phung po rdo rjes gtams byas nas //
NK010(tha)007:117: rnam par shes pa rdo rjer bsgom //
NK010(tha)007:119: sems dang yid dang rnam shes nyid //
NK010(tha)007:120: de nyid las ni 'khrul nas btab //
NK010(tha)007:121: rnam rtog bag chags spang ba'i phyir //
NK010(tha)007:122: bdag dang phur pa gzhal yas khang //
NK010(tha)007:124: rak+ta'i rgya mtsho chen po 'khyil ba'i klong //
NK010(tha)007:125: keng rus chen po'i ri rab brtsegs pa'i steng //
NK010(tha)007:126: rdo rje'i brag chen gtams pa'i sa gzhi la /
NK010(tha)007:127: dur khrod chen po 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang //
NK010(tha)007:128: sus kyang ma bskyed ye nas tshad las 'das //
NK010(tha)007:129: bskal pa me ltar 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor nang //
NK010(tha)007:130: dregs pa lha chen bsnol ba'i gdan stengs su //
NK010(tha)007:131: nyi zla'i gdan bshams pad+ma'i ge sar bcas //
NK010(tha)007:132: tshad dang mtshan nyid ma lus yongs su rdzogs //
NK010(tha)007:133: gtso bo'i gnas su h+aum mthing nag yongs su gyur pa las /
NK010(tha)007:134: 'jigs byed kyi rgyal po dpal rdo rje gzhon nu dbu gsum phyag drug pa /
NK010(tha)007:135: zhabs rnam pa bzhi dang ldan pa /
NK010(tha)007:138: dbus mthing nag tu bzhugs pa /
NK010(tha)007:139: g.yas kyi dang po rdo rje rtse dgu pa dang /
NK010(tha)007:140: g.yon dang po na me dpung 'bar ba bsnams pa /
NK010(tha)007:141: g.yas bar pa na rdo rje rtse lnga pa dang /
NK010(tha)007:144: g.yon bar pa na kha t+w+aam dang /
NK010(tha)007:147: g.yas tha ma na phur pa dang /
NK010(tha)007:148: g.yon tha ma na rbod gtong phra men gyi tshogs bsnams te /
NK010(tha)007:154: zhabs bzhi las gnyis brkyang gnyis bskum ste dor stabs su bzhugs pa'o //
NK010(tha)007:155: sku la bskal pa'i me ri dang /
NK010(tha)007:156: glang po che'i ko rlon dang /
NK010(tha)007:158: zhing chen gyi pags pa dang /
NK010(tha)007:168: thugs rjes chags pa khrag gi rgya mtsho la gsol ba'o //
NK010(tha)007:169: yum 'khor lo rgyas 'debs ma zhal gcig phyag gnyis ma /
NK010(tha)007:170: g.yas yab kyi mgul nas 'khyud pa /
NK010(tha)007:171: g.yon b+han+d+ha rak+tasa bkang nas yab kyi zhal du stobs /
NK010(tha)007:172: sku la dur khrod kyi rgyan gyis brgyan pa /
NK010(tha)007:178: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med par bzhugs pa'o //
NK010(tha)007:180: rdo rje gzhon nu'i rig 'dzin rnams //
NK010(tha)007:181: srid pa rdo rjer grub mdzod cig /
NK010(tha)007:182: srid pa rdo rje phur pa'i lha //
NK010(tha)007:183: ye shes khro bo grub par mdzod //
NK010(tha)007:184: zhes bskul bas srid pa gsum gyi snang zhen rdo
NK010(tha)007:185: rje phur pa'i dkyil 'khor gsum du sgrub pa'i phyir
NK010(tha)007:186: rdo rje chags pa'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par
NK010(tha)007:187: zhugs / yab yum gnyis su med par rdo rje
NK010(tha)007:188: chags pa'i don la bskul bar mdzad de yab kyis
NK010(tha)007:189: sa ma ya hoh yum gyis sa ma ya s+t+wam
NK010(tha)007:190: zhugs / / yab kyis r+aa ho ham /
NK010(tha)007:191: yum gyis r+aa ga ya mi /
NK010(tha)007:192: yab yum gnyis su med par gyur /
NK010(tha)007:193: pad+mo yo gi ni sa ma ya pra be sha ya phata /
NK010(tha)007:194: yab kyi byang chub kyi sems yum gyi mkhar babs te /
NK010(tha)007:195: yum yang byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin du gyur /
NK010(tha)007:196: h+aum h+aum h+aum bi shwa badz+ra kro ta dz+wa la man+da la ha la ha la h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)007:197: ces brjod pas byang chub kyi sems lan gcig 'phros pa khro bo 'chol ba'i rang bzhin du gyur /
NK010(tha)007:198: stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams lhag gis khengs /
NK010(tha)007:199: nyon mongs pa dang log par lta ba'i sems can thams cad bsgral /
NK010(tha)007:200: slar de dag thams cad yum gyi b+ha ga la bsdus te /
NK010(tha)007:201: 'od zer phyogs bcur 'phros pas phyogs bcu'i dregs pa
NK010(tha)007:202: can thams cad bsgral te rtsibs bcur gdan du byas
NK010(tha)007:203: pa'i steng khro bo'i dkyil 'khor 'thon pa ni /
NK010(tha)007:204: h+aum h+aum dzahdzah shar phyogs su khro bo rnam par
NK010(tha)007:205: rgyal ba dbu gsum phyag drug zhabs rnam pa bzhi
NK010(tha)007:206: dang ldan zhing dur khrod kyi chas brgyad kyis brgyan
NK010(tha)007:207: pa / yum rdo rje snyems ma dang 'khril nas
NK010(tha)007:208: brgya byin gyi gdan la brkyang bskum du bzhugs pa'i
NK010(tha)007:209: g.yas su yab kyi sprul pa stag gi mgo can
NK010(tha)007:210: pa / dang / g.yon du yum gyi sprul pa bya rgod kyi mgo can no //
NK010(tha)007:211: h+aum h+aum dzahdzah de bzhin du lhor khro bo gshin rje'i gshed dang /
NK010(tha)007:212: yum dur khrod bdag mo sprul pa sha ba dang 'ug pa'i mgo can /
NK010(tha)007:213: h+aum h+aum dzahdzah nub tu khro bo rta mchog dpal dang yum rdo rje gtum mo //
NK010(tha)007:214: sprul pa byi la dang pu shud mgo can /
NK010(tha)007:215: h+aum h+aum dzahdzah byang du khro bo bdud rtsi 'khyil ba dang yum rdo rje rlung 'byin ma /
NK010(tha)007:216: sprul pa seng ge dang pha wang mgo can /
NK010(tha)007:217: h+aum h+aum dzahdzah shar lhor khro bo dbyug pa sngon po dang yum rdo rje sder mo /
NK010(tha)007:218: sprul pa g.yag dang bya rog mgo can /
NK010(tha)007:219: h+aum h+aum dzahdzah lho nub tu khro bo mi g.yo mgon po dang yum rdo rje gtun khung ma /
NK010(tha)007:220: sprul pa gzig dang khwa ta'i mgo can /
NK010(tha)007:221: h+aum h+aum dzahdzah nub byang du khro bo gzhan gyis
NK010(tha)007:222: mi thub pa dang yum rdo rje mda' snyems ma
NK010(tha)007:223: / sprul pa spyang ki dang khra'i mgo can /
NK010(tha)007:224: h+aum h+aum dzahdzah byang shar du khro bo khams gsum rnam rgyal dang yum rdo rje gsod byed ma /
NK010(tha)007:225: sprul pa dom dang sre mong mgo can /
NK010(tha)007:226: h+aum h+aum dzahdzah steng gi phyogs su khro bo h+aum k+aa ra dang yum rdo rje sgra 'byin ma /
NK010(tha)007:227: sprul pa phag dang smig bu'i mgo can /
NK010(tha)007:228: h+aum h+aum dzahdzah 'og phyogs su khro bo stobs po che dang yum rdo rje bskyod byed ma /
NK010(tha)007:229: sprul pa dred dang byi ba'i mgo can /
NK010(tha)007:230: thams cad kyang rtsa phyag gnyis rdo rje dang dung khrag /
NK010(tha)007:232: tha ma gnyis tir dbyug dang 'dab chags shas cher
NK010(tha)007:233: 'dzin cing dur khrod kyi chas brgyad dang ldan pa'o
NK010(tha)007:235: sangs rgyas kun gyi ye shes sku //
NK010(tha)007:236: ngang nyid rdo rje'i chos dbyings las //
NK010(tha)007:237: 'bar ba'i khro bo mi bzad pa'i //
NK010(tha)007:238: sku yi dbyig tu sras bskyed cig /
NK010(tha)007:239: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba big nan bam h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)007:240: ces brjod pas sras mchog rdzas kyi dkyil 'khor dbu gsum phyag drug pa /
NK010(tha)007:241: sku smad phur pa'i dbal dang ldan pa lnga zla
NK010(tha)007:242: gam gsum la bka' nod pa'i tshul gyis bzhugs pa'o
NK010(tha)007:243: // dzahh+aum bam hohls sgo bzhir sgo ma bzhi dang /
NK010(tha)007:244: mu ran la phur srung dam can gyi tshogs rnams mngon sum lta bur bzhugs pa'o //
NK010(tha)007:245: gnyis pa gnas gsum byin brlab ni /
NK010(tha)007:246: snying ga mgrin pa spyi bo ru //
NK010(tha)007:247: zla ba'i dkyil 'khor bsam nas ni //
NK010(tha)007:250: thugs gsung sku yi rdo rjer bsgom //
NK010(tha)007:251: rdo rje'i phyag rgya gnas gsum du gtug pa dang bstun /
NK010(tha)007:252: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma konya ham /
NK010(tha)007:253: de bzhin du w+aa k+ka dang k+aa ya sbyar /
NK010(tha)007:254: gsum pa dbang bskur ba ni /
NK010(tha)007:255: snying gar gzhal med khang sgo gcig pa'i sgo srung
NK010(tha)007:256: rta mgrin yab yum can gyi nang du gnas pa'i
NK010(tha)007:257: ye shes sems dpa' tshon gang ba bsam la /
NK010(tha)007:258: ye shes dpa' bo'i thugs ka yis //
NK010(tha)007:259: 'od kyis mgon po rnams bskul nas //
NK010(tha)007:260: de dag thugs las byung ba yis //
NK010(tha)007:261: rig mas bdud rtsi bum chu yis //
NK010(tha)007:262: dbang bskur byas te thim gyur nas //
NK010(tha)007:263: rang sngags rdo rje can gyis gzung //
NK010(tha)007:264: dbu rgyan rnams la rigs lnga dang //
NK010(tha)007:265: rigs kyi bdag po rnams kyis brgyan //
NK010(tha)007:267: thabs kyi spyod pas 'gro don du //
NK010(tha)007:268: byams dang snying rjes gang 'dul ba //
NK010(tha)007:269: sangs rgyas phrin las rdzogs mdzad pa //
NK010(tha)007:270: dbang dang byin rlabs bdag stsol cig /
NK010(tha)007:271: rigs lnga'i dbang rgya spyi bor bzhag la /
NK010(tha)007:272: ma h+aa sh+au nya ta dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK010(tha)007:278: bzhi pa khams gsum gyi srog la dbang bskur ba'i
NK010(tha)007:279: sgo nas kyang srid pa phur bur bsgrub pa ni
NK010(tha)007:281: 'gro drug nyon mongs bcings pa rnams //
NK010(tha)007:282: h+aum gis dug chen rab sbyangs te //
NK010(tha)007:283: a n+ri su tri pre dur gyur //
NK010(tha)007:284: ram yam kham las me rlung chus //
NK010(tha)007:285: 'gro ba rab sbyangs h+aum du gyur //
NK010(tha)007:286: khams gsum thams cad rdo rje sems //
NK010(tha)007:287: til gyi gang bu lta bus gang //
NK010(tha)007:288: rta mgrin rgyal po ye shes la //
NK010(tha)007:289: bstim pas byang chub sems rgyas gyur //
NK010(tha)007:290: yab yum gnyis med sbyor ba'i sgras //
NK010(tha)007:291: ye shes khro bo spyan drang ngo //
NK010(tha)007:294: srid pa phur bur bsgrub pa dang //
NK010(tha)007:295: dbang dang dngos grub stsol ba'i phyir //
NK010(tha)007:296: ye shes khro bo gshegs su gsol //
NK010(tha)007:297: khro bo chen po gshegs nas kyang //
NK010(tha)007:298: rtags dang mtshan ma ston pa dang //
NK010(tha)007:299: rdo rje phur pa'i dngos grub stsol //
NK010(tha)007:300: e h+ye hi b+ha ga w+aa na /
NK010(tha)007:301: ma h+aa ka ru ni ka dri sh+ya hoh drug pa bzhugs gsol ni /
NK010(tha)007:303: thugs mchog gsal ba'i byin rlabs las //
NK010(tha)007:304: zhe sdang gnas su 'joms pa dang //
NK010(tha)007:305: me long ye shes 'thob bya'i phyir //
NK010(tha)007:306: dkyil 'khor dbus su bzhugs su gsol //
NK010(tha)007:307: dkyil 'khor dbus su bzhugs nas kyang //
NK010(tha)007:308: nyon mongs mun pa bsal du gsol //
NK010(tha)007:312: yang dag don du sku ni cir snang yang //
NK010(tha)007:313: bdud dang srin po'i nga rgyal ma yin te //
NK010(tha)007:314: 'dul ba'i dbang du rab rngams mche ba gtsigs //
NK010(tha)007:315: h+aum dang phata kyi sgras ni kun kyang bkang //
NK010(tha)007:316: nyon mongs gdug pa 'dul ba'i thugs rje yi //
NK010(tha)007:317: byin rlabs ster ba'i lha la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK010(tha)007:318: a ti pu hoh pra t+aits+tsha hoh brgyad pa mchod pa la spyi dang bye brag gnyis las /
NK010(tha)007:321: bla med mchog gi mchod pa dam pa ni //
NK010(tha)007:322: ye shes lnga yi 'od zer rnam par 'phro //
NK010(tha)007:323: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga yis rab brgyan te //
NK010(tha)007:324: dam tshig bzhin las ci bder bzhes su gsol //
NK010(tha)007:325: sh+r+ai badz+ra ku m+aa ra sa pa ri w+aa ra /
NK010(tha)007:333: shap+ta sarba pany+tsa rak+ta b+ha lim ta kh+aa hi /
NK010(tha)007:334: gnyis pa khyad par rak+ta tshar gsum ni /
NK010(tha)007:336: pho nya la bka' bsgo ba'i don du phul la /
NK010(tha)007:338: dngos grub bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK010(tha)007:339: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK010(tha)007:340: zung zhig rgyob cig rnam par chings //
NK010(tha)007:341: gtogs shig grogs dang bral bar gyis //
NK010(tha)007:342: rengs par khug la smrar chug cig /
NK010(tha)007:343: phob cig rnam par gzir bar gyis //
NK010(tha)007:344: nga yi dbang du gyur nas kyang //
NK010(tha)007:345: bsgo ba'i bka' la nyan par gyis //
NK010(tha)007:347: dam can gnad la dbab phyir phul nas /
NK010(tha)007:349: bran dang bka' nyan pho nya'i tshogs //
NK010(tha)007:350: khyed kyi dam tshig dus la bab //
NK010(tha)007:351: sngon chad ji bzhin bcas pa yi //
NK010(tha)007:352: mngon spyod phrin las myur du mdzod //
NK010(tha)007:354: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul dbrog phyir dbul ba ni /
NK010(tha)007:356: dngos grub bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK010(tha)007:357: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK010(tha)007:359: nga la bar chad byed pa rnams //
NK010(tha)007:360: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul med par mdzod //
NK010(tha)007:364: snang srid thams cad phur pa'i rang bzhin la //
NK010(tha)007:365: khams gsum 'khor ba ming yang mi grags kyang //
NK010(tha)007:366: rgyal ba'i rdzu 'phrul chen po bstan pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)007:367: rdo rje mngon spyod phrin las mdzad la bstod //
NK010(tha)007:370: thugs ka dpal gyi be'u'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK010(tha)007:371: sgo gcig rin chen gzhal yas khang //
NK010(tha)007:372: bde stong gnyis med ngang nyid las //
NK010(tha)007:373: chos kyi sku las longs skur shar //
NK010(tha)007:374: pad+ma zla ba'i gdan la bzhugs //
NK010(tha)007:375: skyon gyis ma gos gti mug sel //
NK010(tha)007:376: yab yum gnyis med zag med sku //
NK010(tha)007:377: sku mdog dkar gsal rnam dag dbyings //
NK010(tha)007:378: rdo rje dril bu phyag na bsnams //
NK010(tha)007:379: shes rab byang chub sems dang ldan //
NK010(tha)007:380: rtog med mi 'gyur skyil krung bzhugs //
NK010(tha)007:381: mkha' dbyings bde chen sku la bstod //
NK010(tha)007:387: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)007:389: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la sarba big nan bam h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)007:391: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba big nan bam h+aum phata dzahh+aum +aa /
NK010(tha)007:392: zhes pa ste dmigs pa'i rim pa ni sgrub thabs rgyas 'bring gnyis kar bstan pas shes so //
NK010(tha)007:393: gsum pa rjes kyi rim pa la bcu gnyis las /
NK010(tha)007:394: dang po tshogs byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK010(tha)007:397: 'byor pa phun sum tshogs byas la //
NK010(tha)007:398: snod ni a las rnam par dag /
NK010(tha)007:399: bcud ni h+aum las bsam par bya //
NK010(tha)007:400: yum gyis 'bar ba'i me bskyod nas //
NK010(tha)007:401: a zhu bcud la thim par gyur //
NK010(tha)007:403: dus gsum rgyal ba'i thugs dam bskul //
NK010(tha)007:404: slar 'dus bdud rtsi nyid du gyur //
NK010(tha)007:409: he ru ka yi gnas bcu dang //
NK010(tha)007:410: dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad nas //
NK010(tha)007:412: dur khrod mchog gi gnas 'di ru //
NK010(tha)007:413: zhing chen gsar rnying ti rar bcas //
NK010(tha)007:416: ma lus gshegs nas bsnams su gsol //
NK010(tha)007:417: badz+ra sa ma ya dzah gsum pa phud dbul ba ni /
NK010(tha)007:419: mthing nag gru gsum 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK010(tha)007:420: bcom ldan rdo rje gzhon nu yab yum dang //
NK010(tha)007:421: phyogs bcu khro rgyal sras mchog za byed tshogs //
NK010(tha)007:422: 'khor gyi dam can bran dang pho nya'i tshogs //
NK010(tha)007:423: dam rdzas tshogs kyi mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NK010(tha)007:424: bar chad med cing gnod pa zhi ba dang //
NK010(tha)007:425: tshogs gnyis rdzogs nas 'bras bu grub par mdzod //
NK010(tha)007:426: g+ha na tsakra p+au tsa kh+aa hi /
NK010(tha)007:429: mkha' 'gro ma dang sha za mo //
NK010(tha)007:430: ra ro ma dang khrag 'thung ma //
NK010(tha)007:431: sa bla sa 'og sa steng gi //
NK010(tha)007:432: las la grub pa'i mkha' 'gro'i tshogs //
NK010(tha)007:433: gtor ma len cing las rnams byed //
NK010(tha)007:434: mnyam par rol pa'i bde chen gyis //
NK010(tha)007:435: dpa' bo dpa' mo mnyes gyur cig /
NK010(tha)007:436: spro dang bsdu ba'i bde ba yis //
NK010(tha)007:437: mkha' 'gro ma tshogs tshim gyur cig /
NK010(tha)007:438: bdud rtsi lnga ldan tshogs mchod kyis //
NK010(tha)007:440: mkha' 'gro ma tshogs mnyes gyur nas //
NK010(tha)007:441: dam tshig nyams chag dag par mdzod //
NK010(tha)007:445: dam tshig chen po'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)007:446: tshogs kyi bsgral mchod bzhes su gsol //
NK010(tha)007:447: sprul pa chen po'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)007:448: tshogs kyi bsgral mchod bzhes su gsol //
NK010(tha)007:449: phyag brnyan chen po'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)007:450: tshogs kyi bsgral mchod bzhes su gsol //
NK010(tha)007:451: gdug cir sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK010(tha)007:453: nga la bar gcod byed pa rnams //
NK010(tha)007:454: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul med par mdzod //
NK010(tha)007:458: shwa na mu kha'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)007:459: lhag ma'i gtor ma bzhes su gsol //
NK010(tha)007:460: bka' yi gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK010(tha)007:461: rnal 'byor bar chad bsrung du gsol //
NK010(tha)007:462: sa bdag chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)007:463: lhag ma'i gtor ma bzhes su gsol //
NK010(tha)007:464: bka' yi gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK010(tha)007:465: rnal 'byor bar chad bsrung du gsol //
NK010(tha)007:466: bdag nyid chen mo'i dus la bab //
NK010(tha)007:467: lhag ma'i gtor ma bzhes su gsol //
NK010(tha)007:468: bka' yi gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK010(tha)007:469: rnal 'byor bar chad bsrung du gsol //
NK010(tha)007:470: kha nas khrag dang zhag 'dzag cing //
NK010(tha)007:471: lag pa thod khrag thogs nas ni //
NK010(tha)007:472: hi hir dgod cing spyugs pa 'bod //
NK010(tha)007:473: ma bdun sring bzhi la sogs pa //
NK010(tha)007:474: phur srung rnams kyi dus la bab //
NK010(tha)007:475: lhag ma'i gtor ma bzhes su gsol //
NK010(tha)007:476: bka' yi gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK010(tha)007:477: rnal 'byor bar chad bsrung du gsol //
NK010(tha)007:480: bla ma la gus snying rje ldan //
NK010(tha)007:481: rdo rje gzhon nu grub nas kyang //
NK010(tha)007:482: skye shi med par 'gyur bar shog /
NK010(tha)007:483: zab mo'i don la sems pa dang //
NK010(tha)007:484: btsun mo'i khu ba mnyam zas can //
NK010(tha)007:485: skye zhing skye bar 'gyur bar shog /
NK010(tha)007:488: rkang pa brkyang bar mi bya zhing //
NK010(tha)007:489: phyi rol gtam yang rab tu spangs //
NK010(tha)007:490: mi dgod gsang ba'i ngag la gnas //
NK010(tha)007:491: dam tshig med cing ngang rgyud ngan //
NK010(tha)007:492: rtog pa can la tshogs 'khor gsang //
NK010(tha)007:493: rdo rje'i glu ni rab tu blang //
NK010(tha)007:494: mkha' 'gro rnams la gtor ma byin //
NK010(tha)007:500: bcu gnyis pa bkra shis rnams sgrub thabs 'bring po ltar bya'o //
NK010(tha)007:501: skye gnas bzhi yi bag chags sbyong tshul la //
NK010(tha)007:502: go ba ma rnyed gong nas spros pa dor //
NK010(tha)007:503: sbyang gzhi sbyong byed med pa'i krong bskyed la //
NK010(tha)007:504: sngags pa brjod la 'di yang mngas kyi dogs //
NK010(tha)007:505: de lta na'ang legs byas nyin mo'i dpal //
NK010(tha)007:506: yang dag ltar snang 'byed pa'i mig ldan du //
NK010(tha)007:507: gyur nas snga 'gyur ring lugs pad+ma'i tshal //
